.TH SIMPLE_SHELL 1 "December 2024" "1.0" "Simple Shell - Holberton School"
.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a simple Unix shell

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B simple_shell
.RI [ options ]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B simple_shell
is a basic Unix shell that provides a command line interface for users to interact with the operating system.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-h, \-\-help
Display this help and exit.

.SH USAGE
The simple shell can execute commands, handle input and output redirection, and run built-in shell commands.

.SH EXAMPLES
Run the shell:
.EX
$ ./simple_shell
.EX

Execute a command:
.EX
$ ls -l
.EX

.SH AUTHOR
Written by Luca Mansi.

